Interface InternalNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLayout, LithoLayoutResult, YogaNode.Inputs
    All Known Subinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface InternalNode
extends YogaNode.Inputs, LithoLayoutResult
    Internal class representing a ComponentLayout.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  InternalNode.NestedTreeHolder
      The API for the nested tree holder, which is used to hold the partial results of an unresolved node which will be resolved after layout calculation for components which implement OnCreateLayoutWithSizeSpec.
